//! Purpose:
//! Baked `name,mask,cc` timezone table backing `DateTimeZone::listIdentifiers()`
//! group/country filtering (and the `timezone_identifiers_list()` alias). Each
//! row is `identifier,groupMask,countryCode` joined by `;`; rows joined likewise.
//!
//! Called from:
//! - `crate::list_id_prelude` to splice into the `__elephc_list_identifiers`
//!   prelude function body.
//!
//! Key details:
//! - Data only. Captured from PHP 8.5 (`DateTimeZone::listIdentifiers`/`getLocation`)
//!   so membership, group masks, country codes, and the ALL_WITH_BC row order are
//!   byte-exact with PHP. `groupMask` ORs the region-group bits (AFRICA=1 ..
//!   UTC=1024); bit 2048 marks a backward-compat (BC) zone present only in
//!   ALL_WITH_BC (4095), never in ALL (2047). Filtering is `(mask & group) != 0`,
//!   or `countryCode === arg` when the PER_COUNTRY (4096) bit is set.

/// One row per IANA zone in ALL_WITH_BC order: `identifier,groupMask,countryCode`,
